# NPM Configuration for GitHub Packages
# Copy this file to .npmrc and replace the environment variable with your actual token

@juaose:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_NPM_TOKEN}

# For local development, you can replace ${GITHUB_NPM_TOKEN} with your actual GitHub token
# Example:
# //npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=ghp_your_actual_token_here

# To generate a GitHub token:
# 1. Go to GitHub Settings > Developer settings > Personal access tokens
# 2. Generate a new token with 'read:packages' permission
# 3. Use that token in place of ${GITHUB_NPM_TOKEN}
